  <div class="attachment-details">
    <h2 class="title"><a href="/government/publications/extension-to-the-coronavirus-job-retention-scheme/extension-of-the-coronavirus-job-retention-scheme">Extension of the Coronavirus Job Retention Scheme</a></h2>
    <p class="metadata">
        <span class="type">HTML</span>
    </p>


  </div>
</section>

</div>

  </section>



      <section id="details">
        <h2 class="gem-c-heading gem-c-heading--font-size-27 gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  ">Details</h2>


        
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
    
          <div class="govspeak">
<p>The Coronavirus Job Retention Scheme (<abbr title="Coronavirus Job Retention Scheme">CJRS</abbr>) will remain open until 31 March 2021.</p>

<div role="note" aria-label="Information" class="application-notice info-notice">
<p>This policy paper applies to <abbr title="Coronavirus Job Retention Scheme">CJRS</abbr> claims for periods starting on or after 1 November 2020.</p>
</div>

<p>Claims relating to periods ending on or before 31 October 2020 are not part of this extension. For claims on or before this date <a href="https://www.gov.uk/guidance/claim-for-wage-costs-through-the-coronavirus-job-retention-scheme" class="govuk-link">check the existing guidance for more information</a>.</p>

</div>

</div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div class="app-c-published-dates " lang="en">
    Published 5 November 2020
